{"tid":2250426,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大法官鄭念慈：「所有警員證人皆誠實可靠」，裁定所有被告罪名成立","createTime":"2020-10-20T05:52:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-29T10:46:25.000Z","uid":230104,"like":3,"dislike":95,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"a9e6993204118fbc57ea2fe63bcf6252521a337b","tid":2250426,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T05:52:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4odAUTF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4odAUTF.jpg&h=6da47758&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去年8月3日網民發起旺角大遊行，追究警方濫權，逾12萬市民出席，至晚上演變成警民衝突，9人事後被控非法集結罪，其中一名16歲男生同時被控管有攻擊性武器。裁判官鄭念慈今裁決指，所有警員證人皆誠實可靠，並憑呈堂片段及各被告當時的衣著和裝備，推論他們均為現場參與集結的示威者，裁定所有被告罪名成立。鄭官更強調，即使沒有證據顯示被告何時在現場出現或做出甚麼行為，但他們參與的集結必然為非法集結。較年輕的五名被告等候報告始判，其間還柙；另四人判監4個月，但准保釋等候上訴。<br />\n<br />\n首被告另被控於同日同地管有攻擊性武器，<span class=\"red\">即一支雷射筆。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201019/UOWSV7AUOFEKHEAS73CG3MEALQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201019%2FUOWSV7AUOFEKHEAS73CG3MEALQ%2F&d=h9s%2FmsO%2BhBO0acKdDJaYEbuZPUOKbERJWvoN25G5CUI%3D&h=caad0818\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201019%2FUOWSV7AUOFEKHEAS73CG3MEALQ%2F&h=85fe4da2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201019/UOWSV7AUOFEKHEAS73CG3MEALQ/</a>"},{"pid":"d375dbe019be02493b7815ea36e6b8c726420ffc","tid":2250426,"uid":141024,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T05:53:50.000Z","msg":"狗官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0e60d65b5f77201c70a3d332bb98302fead5379","tid":2250426,"uid":19552,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T05:55:11.000Z","msg":"出晒名啦呢條柒頭"},{"pid":"b433439f9490d15d93c67603e647f39c2cfcf48d","tid":2250426,"uid":230104,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T05:56:28.000Z","msg":"鄭念慈+鄭紀航，林鄭保駕